'''Fikile Mthwalo''' (yavutse ku ya 13 Mata 1989), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri  [[Lesoto|Lesotho]] wavukiye [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] akaba n'umwanditsi wa firime . <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=17252</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri serial zizwi ''Biragoye'', ''Isidingo'' na ''Gold Diggers'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/truelove/Archive/4-things-we-learned-about-fikile-mthwalo-kani-20170728</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 13 Mata 1989 i Lesotho kwa se wa Mosotho na nyina wa [[Kenya]] / [[Tanzaniya|Tanzaniya.]] <ref name="okmzansi">https://okmzansi.co.za/6-things-didnt-know-fikile-mthwalo/</ref> Afite murumunawe utuye Cape Town . Kuva mu 2001 kugeza 2005, yize muri Machabeng International College ifite icyicaro i [[Maseru]] . Nyuma yimukiye i Bloemfontein, muri Afurika yepfo arangiza Matric muri 2007, mu ishuri rya St Michael Girls. Mu 2009, yinjiye muri kaminuza ya Cape Town arangiza impamyabumenyi ya Bachelor of Arts Film na Video Production. <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/42113-fikile-mthwalo-bio-age-pregnancy-hubby-alleged-separation-pictures-instagram.html</ref> Nyuma muri 2012, yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye na Filime mu ishuri ry’ubuhanzi rya Tisch muri kaminuza ya New York. Amaze kubona impamyabumenyi, yimukiye i Johannesburg . <ref>https://zalebs.com/drama/fikile-mthwalo/close-and-personal-fikile-mthwalo</ref>

Yashakanye na mugenzi we wo muri Afurika yepfo Atandwa Kani kuva ku ya 24 Ukuboza 2015. Yahuye na Kani mugihe cya tereviziyo aho basezeranye barashyingirwa nyuma yumwaka. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/News/i-am-atandwas-first-wife-fikile-mthwalo-kani-20170728</ref> Bateguye ubukwe bwabo gakondo 'Lobolo' nyuma yubukwe bwabo. Atandwa ni umuhungu wa John Kani na Mandi Kani. Mbere yubukwe bwabo, Kani yari afitanye umubano numuntu witangazamakuru, Thembisa Mdoda. Bombi baratandukanye nyuma yimyaka itatu. <ref name="briefly" />

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina muri opera izwi cyane, ''Isidingo'' . Yabaye umwe mu barangije hejuru 24 mu 'O Access Presenter Search' amakuba zicishwa kuri umuyoboro O. Mu 2015, yatumye we mbere televiziyo iya uruhare na gukina imico 'Ipeleng' mu serial ''It’s Complicated.'' Usibye ibyo, yinjiye mu matangazo yamamaza kuri tereviziyo harimo Metropolitan, PEP, Omo, Shoprite, Etiselat Nigeria, Ibidendezi, Hi-Malt Nigeria na Nivea UK. Yagaragaye muri telenovela ''Gold Diggers'' aho yakinnye nka 'Hlengiwe'.  

== Uburezi ==
Fikile yabonye impamyabumenyi ya Bachelors muri Film na Video Production yakuye muri kaminuza ya Cape Town (UCT), ari naho yarangirije icyubahiro muri 2012. Muri 2015 yahawe buruse yuzuye yo kwitabira gahunda yo gukina amanota ya kaminuza ya New York [https://tisch.nyu.edu/grad-acting (NYU)] . Muri 2018 yarangije Masters mu buhanzi Bwiza (MFA) mu gukina.

